title: Kafe Spesial
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Pizza, Italian, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Popular with students and packed on weekends, this place keeps soymilk on hand for chai tea latte. Has a quinoa burger (vegan when omit aioli) and house-made fruit sorbet. Pizza can be ordered without cheese, but first inquire about the crust. Wide selections of beers and ciders, some of which are vegan, and even organic such as Dunkerton's cider.
